{"title":"山乡，响起春的足音（外一首）","authors":["马辉"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":2,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山乡，响起春的足音（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那抿嘴儿笑的村姑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正搂着三月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诉说着攒了一篓子的悄悄话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，春来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏绿了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北方的阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡土，我读不够的书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写满大豆水稻高梁小麦的乡土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舒展着神奇传说的乡土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镶着野菊花边儿的乡土呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我最爱读的书——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它会解释爷爷的脸为什么老是阴沉沉的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它会解释爸爸的笑为什么是泥色的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它会解释我的梦为什么会溢满芳馨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这城市喧哗的夜晚中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我用泪珠子读着它"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫瘠的心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便长满了怀念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我读不够的书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}